WHAT'S THE MATTER, EUREKA?

133
00:08:34,333 --> 00:08:35,416
ARE YOU ALL RIGHT?

134
00:08:35,500 --> 00:08:37,166
- ALL RIGHT NOW,
WHAT'S GOING ON HERE?

135
00:08:39,208 --> 00:08:40,916
- SHE'S HAVING
TROUBLE ESTABLISHING

