WITH RENTON.

137
00:08:43,333 --> 00:08:45,416
- YOU MEAN THEY'RE NOT...
COMMUNICATING?

138
00:08:45,500 --> 00:08:47,291
- YOU KNOW WHAT THAT MEANS.

139
00:08:48,666 --> 00:08:49,875
- IF YOU DON'T WANT TO DO IT,

140
00:08:49,958 --> 00:08:52,000
