FOR YOU TO SAY NO.

141
00:08:52,083 --> 00:08:54,833
- IF HE'S PERSISTENT ABOUT IT,
YOU CAN JUST PUNCH HIM!

142
00:08:54,916 --> 00:08:56,416
- WHAT ARE YOU
TALKING ABOUT, GIDGET?

143
00:08:58,041 --> 00:09:01,541
